cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA 

The paper focuses on the application of deep reinforcement learning (RL) in traffic signal control, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multi-agent RL (MARL) also suggests the relevance to robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for decentralized MARL, which is a subfield of multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
